{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>You are a hacker detective of justice.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become a <u>hacker detective to</u> solve people's problems... and solve what they ask you to do!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">People have a wide variety of requests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And to solve their requests..,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>The solution is hacking.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To solve the requests... <strong>Hacking</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hack and analyze the PC!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And... <u>Find the source of the client's problems in the PC and solve them!</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The PC you hack may or may not belong to the client...?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Solve the mystery and hack!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And how to hack... <u>Solving riddles</u>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve the wide variety of riddles that stand in your way and solve the requests!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Overview</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is a <u>riddle solving adventure</u>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It will be released <u>as a free game</u>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The difficulty level of the riddles will change depending on the client. The game can be enjoyed by everyone from puzzle-solving beginners to advanced solvers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>About distribution and play-by-play</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are welcome to distribute and play the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No prior notice is required. Monetization is also OK.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357980/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736674767","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st